.contents
  .message_main 3行ポジティブ日記 〜ポジティブなことを書き出そう！〜
  - if user_signed_in?
    .user_nav.grid-7
      - @messages.each do |message|
        .contents__post 
          %ul.text_list
            %li.message_text1
              = message.text1
            %li.message_text2
              = message.text2
            %li.message_text3
              = message.text3
          .message_info
            .message_time
              = message.created_at.strftime("%Y年%m月%d日")
            .message_image
              = image_tag message.image.url, size: "55x55", alt: "face", claas: "face_image"
              -# = message.image
  - else 
    .user_nav.grid-8
      .user_nav_image
        = image_tag 'diary.jpeg', alt: "画像", class: "img"
      .user_nav_message
        新規登録をして3行ポジティブ日記を始めよう！